  "calendar": [],
  "general_provisions": "This bill supplements or reduces appropriations otherwise provided for the support and operation of state government for the fiscal year beginning July 1, 2026 and ending June 30, 2027.",
  "hilighted_provisions": "This bill:<hr><ltbullet>provides budget increases and decreases for the use and support of certain state agencies;<hr><ltbullet>provides budget increases and decreases for the use and support of certain institutions of higher education;<hr><ltbullet>provides budget increases and decreases for other purposes as described;<hr><ltbullet>authorizes full time employment levels for certain internal service funds; and<hr><ltbullet>provides intent language.",
